{"tid":1829706,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"新國殤之柱 撐港抗爭者","createTime":"2020-01-19T04:05:13.000Z","updateTime":"2020-01-19T04:19:09.000Z","uid":25558,"like":8,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":8,"replies":[{"pid":"734c514d63dc7ed4a84dc3a1aa7ea51d1bdb337b","tid":1829706,"uid":25558,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-19T04:05:13.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://hk.news.appledaily.com/local/20200119/NJPB5LAX3NF7M2FCAGN2ADWXD4/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20200119%2FNJPB5LAX3NF7M2FCAGN2ADWXD4%2F&d=hCh8nFxZocjAH0BHn0nK1Ev%2FgUeHX8FRhdV3zHjzpFI%3D&h=b39c0c28\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20200119%2FNJPB5LAX3NF7M2FCAGN2ADWXD4%2F&h=cdb4eace\" target=\"_blank\">https://hk.news.appledaily.com/local/20200119/NJPB5LAX3NF7M2FCAGN2ADWXD4/</a><br />\n<br />\n新國殤之柱 撐港抗爭者<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://static.appledaily.hk/images/apple-photos/apple/20200119/large/1579365090_c422.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.appledaily.hk%2Fimages%2Fapple-photos%2Fapple%2F20200119%2Flarge%2F1579365090_c422.jpg&h=ec5b7333&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n新國殤之柱高八米，將於丹麥國會外豎立。<br />\n(社內相)<br />\n<br />\n【本報訊】曾製作「國殤之柱」的丹麥藝術家高志活，為聲討中共對港人的可恥行為及聲援港人，將於本周四在位於哥本哈根的丹麥國會外豎立八米高、以香港抗爭者為主角的「新國殤之柱」，柱形雕塑並配以四個戴上頭盔、眼罩、防毒面具、代表香港抗爭者的頭像。<br />\n<br />\n相關新聞：鄭文傑寄語港人「用盡手段爭民主」<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n周四揭幕 港人發言<br />\n<br />\n新國殤之柱於丹麥時間本周四中午揭幕，屆時高志活將與曾聲援香港抗爭的丹麥政黨The Alternative，以及丹麥國際特赦組織也會出席，高志活和身在丹麥、支持反修例運動的港人也會到場發言。<br />\n<br />\n新國殤之柱的設計，如現時擺放在港大、紀念六四屠城的國殤之柱般，柱身由多個不同形態兼扭曲的身體雕塑組成，同時特別加入代表香港抗爭者的頭像，四個頭像如香港抗爭者般，戴上頭盔、眼罩及防毒面具。<br />\n<br />\n高志活表示，西方社會對港人的支持，有份確保港人享有言論自由的機會及和平集會的權利。<br />\n<br />\n政黨The Alternative一直有留意香港反送中運動，該黨領袖Uffe Elbak指，合力將新國殤之柱展示於國會外，是要表達該黨對港人的支持，香港的反修例運動正是世界不同地方人權受壓的寫照。他又指政權透過人臉識別系統來打壓言論自由和集會自由，該黨在丹麥正想將這些極權手法列為不合法。<br />\n<br />\n■記者呂浩然<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://static.appledaily.hk/images/apple-photos/apple/20200119/large/1579365089_b66d.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.appledaily.hk%2Fimages%2Fapple-photos%2Fapple%2F20200119%2Flarge%2F1579365089_b66d.jpg&h=fd1f3c1d&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n雕塑四側配以代表香港抗爭者的頭像。<br />\n(社內相)"},{"pid":"65e43782ac2f51f7c7aefff67553592d18fd38c7","tid":1829706,"uid":25558,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-19T04:05:28.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://static.appledaily.hk/images/apple-photos/apple/20200119/large/1579365089_b66d.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.appledaily.hk%2Fimages%2Fapple-photos%2Fapple%2F20200119%2Flarge%2F1579365089_b66d.jpg&h=fd1f3c1d&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n雕塑四側配以代表香港抗爭者的頭像。<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"81551137221acfbcd5e928eea17d4269fb313969","tid":1829706,"uid":175623,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-19T04:08:58.000Z","msg":"今天不出來 下次出不來 珍惜集會遊行自由<br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/eLOGoS\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/eLOGoS</a>"},{"pid":"8937833e3ecfd38a4ebf7073c598b65d38cf859e","tid":1829706,"uid":268519,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-19T04:09:09.000Z","msg":"Twitter<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n創作人：<a href=\"https://t